### Transfers Module REST Client Tests

### Process delivery payments
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/transfers/process-delivery-payments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "order_id": 123,
  "delivery_id": 456,
  "store": {
    "id": "store123",
    "name": "Sample Store",
    "account_number": "0712345678",
    "amount": 800,
    "participantType": "store"
  },
  "driver": {
    "id": "driver456",
    "name": "John Doe",
    "account_number": "0787654321",
    "amount": 200,
    "participantType": "driver"
  }
}

### Verify transfer status
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/transfers/verify/{{transfer_reference}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Get transfers by order ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/transfers/order/{{order_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Get transfers by delivery ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/transfers/delivery/{{delivery_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
